ss. Learn and apply QA methodologies, testing techniques, and best practices. Ask questions and seekPlease mention the word **AWE** and tag RMjQwOTo0MGYyOjEwNGI6ZmMwZDpkZGFhOjc0Yjg6NzkxNTo1ZTIx when applying to show you read the job post completely (#RMjQwOTo0MGYyOjEwNGI6ZmMwZDpkZGFhOjc0Yjg6NzkxNTo1ZTIx). This is a beta feature to avoid spam applicants. Companies can search these words to find applicants that read this and see they\'re human.', 'technical, testing, test, web, qa, financial, junior, engineer', 'Not specified', 1, 0, 'OFF', 'open', '2026-03-27 12:15:51', 'Full-time', NULL, NULL),
